items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 250 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 51!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 175 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 36!
Light and crisp, a Pilsner is all you need to make your day great. Though, perhaps another one would make it even better. That’s 10 different Pilsners. Try 5 more to unlock level 3.
Light and crisp, a Pilsner is all you need to make your day great. Though, perhaps another one would make it even better. That’s 20 different Pilsners. Try 5 more to unlock Level 5.

It’s official - you are part of history! Untappd has reached its one billionth check-in of all time. Cheers to our global family of users and let’s raise a beer to many, many more! #checkinlife #onebillionbeers
